la sobre las coyunturas inflamadas.&nbsp;</span></p>', 'active', 5, 6, 'beneficios-de-la-manzanilla-aqui-te-ensenamos-secretos-imperdibles', '2017-07-18 01:45:20', '2017-07-29 21:45:11'),
(20, 'Tratamientos cosméticos con Pepino', '<p style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0in; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; word-break: normal;"><span style="font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:+mn-ea;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:+mn-cs;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:\r\n12.0pt;language:es-AR;mso-style-textfill-type:solid;mso-style-textfill-fill-color:\r\n#333333;mso-style-textfill-fill-alpha:100.0%">El pepino tienen muchas\r\npropiedades que ayudan a mejorar la apariencia de </span><span style="font-size:14.0pt;font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:+mn-ea;mso-bidi-font-family:+mn-cs;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;\r\ncolor:#333333;mso-font-kerning:12.0pt;language:es-AR;mso-style-textfill-type:\r\nsolid;mso-style-textfill-fill-color:#333333;mso-style-textfill-fill-alpha:100.0%">la\r\n</span><span style="font-size:14.0pt;font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-fareast-font-family:+mn-ea;mso-bidi-font-family:+mn-cs;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;\r\ncolor:#333333;mso-font-kerning:12.0pt;language:es-AR;mso-style-textfill-type:\r\nsolid;mso-style-textfill-fill-color:#333333;mso-style-textfill-fill-alpha:100.0%">piel,\r\npor ejemplo bajando la hinchazón, la sensación de cansancio y </span><span style="font-size:14.0pt;font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:+mn-ea;mso-bidi-font-family:+mn-cs;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;\r\ncolor:#333333;mso-font-kerning:12.0pt;language:es-AR;mso-style-textfill-type:\r\nsolid;mso-style-textfill-fill-color:#333333;mso-style-textfill-fill-alpha:100.0%">también\r\n</span><span style="font-size:14.0pt;font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-fareast-font-family:+mn-ea;mso-bidi-font-family:+mn-cs;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;\r\ncolor:#333333;mso-font-kerning:12.0pt;language:es-AR;mso-style-textfill-type:\r\nsolid;mso-style-textfill-fill-color:#333333;mso-style-textfill-fill-alpha:100.0%">favoreciendo\r\n</span><span style="font-size:14.0pt;font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-fareast-font-family:+mn-ea;mso-bidi-font-family:+mn-cs;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;\r\ncolor:#333333;mso-font-kerning:12.0pt;language:es-AR;mso-style-textfill-type:\r\nsolid;mso-style-textfill-fill-color:#333333;mso-style-textfill-fill-alpha:100.0%">la\r\ndesaparición de manchas y cicatrices. </span><span style="font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:+mn-ea;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:+mn-cs;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:\r\n12.0pt;language:es-AR;mso-style-textfill-type:solid;mso-style-textfill-fill-color:\r\n#333333;mso-style-textfill-fill-alpha:100.0%">Para esto tenemos que hacer una\r\nmascarilla, aquí van los consejos de como hacerlo en 5 minutos:</span></p><span style="font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:+mn-ea;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:+mn-cs;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:\r\n12.0pt;language:es-AR;mso-style-textfill-type:solid;mso-style-textfill-fill-color:\r\n#333333;mso-style-textfill-fill-alpha:100.0%"><br></span>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0in; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; word-break: normal;"><span style="font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:+mn-ea;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:+mn-cs;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:\r\n12.0pt;language:es-AR;font-weight:bold;mso-style-textfill-type:solid;\r\nmso-style-textfill-fill-color:#333333;mso-style-textfill-fill-alpha:100.0%">Para\r\nhidratar la piel: </span><font color="#333333" face="Calibri"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">necesitamos triturar ½ pepino,\r\nagregar una cucharada de aceite y dos de miel, mezclar bien y extender la\r\nmezcla sobre la cara y dejar actuar unos 20 minutos, </span><span style="font-size: 18.6667px;">después</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;">&nbsp;limpiamos con agua\r\ntibia.</span></font></p><span style="font-size:14.0pt;font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:+mn-ea;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n+mn-cs;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:12.0pt;\r\nlanguage:es-AR;mso-style-textfill-type:solid;mso-style-textfill-fill-color:\r\n#333333;mso-style-textfill-fill-alpha:100.0%"><br></span>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0in; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; word-break: normal;"><span style="font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:+mn-ea;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:+mn-cs;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:\r\n12.0pt;language:es-AR;font-weight:bold;mso-style-textfill-type:solid;\r\nmso-style-textfill-fill-color:#333333;mso-style-textfill-fill-alpha:100.0%">Para\r\nbajar la hinchazón de los ojos</span><span style="font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:+mn-ea;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:+mn-cs;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:\r\n12.0pt;language:es-AR;mso-style-textfill-type:solid;mso-style-textfill-fill-color:\r\n#333333;mso-style-textfill-fill-alpha:100.0%">:</span><span style="font-size:\r\n14.0pt;font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n+mn-ea;mso-bidi-font-family:+mn-cs;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:\r\n12.0pt;language:es-AR;mso-style-textfill-type:solid;mso-style-textfill-fill-color:\r\n#333333;mso-style-textfill-fill-alpha:100.0%"> cortamos 2 rodajas las dejamos\r\nsobre los ojos cerrados durante dos minutos y listo!</span></p><span style="font-size:\r\n14.0pt;font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n+mn-ea;mso-bidi-font-family:+mn-cs;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:\r\n12.0pt;language:es-AR;mso-style-textfill-type:solid;mso-style-textfill-fill-color:\r\n#333333;mso-style-textfill-fill-alpha:100.0%"><br></span>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0in; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; word-break: normal;"><span style="font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:+mn-ea;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:+mn-cs;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:\r\n12.0pt;language:es-AR;font-weight:bold;mso-style-textfill-type:solid;\r\nmso-style-textfill-fill-color:#333333;mso-style-textfill-fill-alpha:100.0%">Para\r\ncombatir el acné: </span><span style="font-size:14.0pt;font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:+mn-ea;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n+mn-cs;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:12.0pt;\r\nlanguage:es-AR;mso-style-textfill-type:solid;mso-style-textfill-fill-color:\r\n#333333;mso-style-textfill-fill-alpha:100.0%">mezclar medio pepino triturado\r\ncon 2 cucharadas avena, 2 de miel, 1 cuchara sopera de jugo de limón, aplicar\r\nhacienda círculos en la cara, dejar actual 10 minutos y retirar con agua tibia.</span></p>', 'active', 5, 8, 'tratamientos-cosmeticos-con-pepino', '2017-07-19 04:47:14', '2017-07-29 21:48:48');
