span></p>\r\n\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="ES-TRAD" style="font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Symbol">·<span style="font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><strong><span lang="ES-TRAD">Aceites emulsionables<o:p></o:p></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph"><u><span lang="ES-TRAD">Preparación</span></u><span lang="ES-TRAD">: se disuelve una cucharadita en un litro de agua.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph"><u><span lang="ES-TRAD">Aplicación</span></u><span lang="ES-TRAD">:\r\nse pulveriza sobre las plantas.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph"><u><span lang="ES-TRAD">Control</span></u><span lang="ES-TRAD">:\r\npulgones, cochinillas, ácaros, mosca blanca.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<span lang="ES-TRAD">&nbsp;</span>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="ES-TRAD" style="font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Symbol">·<span style="font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><strong><span lang="ES-TRAD">Piretrinas<o:p></o:p></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph"><u><span lang="ES-TRAD">Preparación</span></u><span lang="ES-TRAD">: se mezcla 1 gr o 5-10 cm3 en un litro de agua.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph"><u><span lang="ES-TRAD">Aplicación</span></u><span lang="ES-TRAD">:\r\nse pulveriza sobre las plantas.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph"><u><span lang="ES-TRAD">Control</span></u><span lang="ES-TRAD">:\r\npulgones, trips, hormigas, chinches, orugas, isocas, moscas de los frutos.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<span lang="ES-TRAD">&nbsp;</span>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="ES-TRAD" style="font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Symbol">·<span style="font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><strong><span lang="ES-TRAD">Polisulfuro de calcio<o:p></o:p></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph"><u><span lang="ES-TRAD">Preparación</span></u><span lang="ES-TRAD">: se mezcla un litro de producto formulado en diez litros de agua.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph"><u><span lang="ES-TRAD">Aplicación</span></u><span lang="ES-TRAD">:\r\nse pulveriza sobre las plantas.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph"><u><span lang="ES-TRAD">Control</span></u><span lang="ES-TRAD">:\r\npulgones, cochinillas, ácaros y como fungicida para oidio. Se puede emplear\r\ncomo cicatrizante.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<span lang="ES-TRAD">&nbsp;</span>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="text-align:justify;text-justify:\